column5: You are so busy you forget to take pics. We were up on one of the small iced up marinas today. Started off slow, but when they suddenly turned on I could not keep up with the 2 rods.  30-40 dinks and enough for a generous supper before I called it a day.  But it is only a tall tale without fish porn so I went out and built me a school
Was there any Alexander Keith's harmed in the making of that school?
I value my fingers too much   Mind you AK is taking a severe beating at this very moment. The life is literally draining right out of him
pretty cool stuff.... i think im gunna make a few tomorrow just for the heck of it. gotta get rid of that wood some how!

Nothing wrong with that. A work buddy gave me some homemade red wine...Merlot I think...to sample. Good stuff, but only one bottle  Got some maxwell house brewing right now to take it's place. BTW up our way it was on sale this week at Loblaws Superstore. Thanks for the coffee tip earlier this week my friend.
Those little fishies look like the ones I caught last weekend... give them back please  I need them for "evidence" that I was actually fishing
i just learned that cardboard tastes like eggs and mayonnaise ....i wonder what those fish will taste like ...
With the right additives thrown in... No different than a McDusty burger
